# Spotify app credentials for Clipify (https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard)
# Production redirect URI: https://kesav-v.github.io/
# Local dev: use a fixed HTTP loopback URI already saved in your Spotify app, e.g.:
#   REACT_APP_SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI=http://127.0.0.1:8888/callback
# Then run: npm run start:clipify
REACT_APP_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here
REACT_APP_SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI=http://127.0.0.1:8888/callback
